---
title: Layered Creamy Chicken Breast Pasta Bake  with Tomato Sauce, Courgette and Cheese
description: This Layered Creamy Chicken Breast Pasta Bake  is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF-Y23-R01-W16-UK-R1622-58-Main-low-EDIT-courgette-MOD-2a0ec3b5.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/layered-creamy-chicken-breast-pasta-bake-63f36c6eb6ae9e66039dd708-4e6ce7c7.pdf
